</P>
<P>
   At Arlington, Texas, Ivan Rodriguez said his bruised right elbow
was fine, then proved it by going 3-for-3 with a home run. The
reigning AL MVP was drilled by a pitch Thursday night in a game
against Double-A Tulsa. Once learning X-rays were negative,
Rodriguez wasted no time getting back behind the plate.
