that we must take politics out of this decision,'' said Clinton Senate campaign
spokesman Howard Wolfson. ''Elian's future should be determined as quickly as
possible through the appropriate, ongoing legal process.'' Clinton's position on
Elian also put her at odds with New York City Mayor Rudolph Giuliani, who
